msgid ""
"\n"
"    Archivos pequeños asociados al issue (capturas, logs, notas…). Se "
"guardan en base64 dentro de la base de\n"
"    datos; tamaño máximo 5 MB.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"\nSmall files attached to an issue (screenshots, logs, notes…). Stored as base64 in the database;\n    maximum size 5 MB."

msgid "Time tracking"
msgstr "Time tracking"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Cada issue tiene una estimación (en minutos) y se le pueden ir "
"registrando work logs según se avanza.\n"
"    El panel lateral muestra <em>tiempo registrado / estimado</em> y la "
"lista de logs recientes.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"\nEach issue has an estimate (in minutes) and work logs can be recorded as progress is made.\n    The side panel shows <em>logged time / estimate</em> and the list of recent logs."

msgid "Issue links"
msgstr "Issue links"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Relaciones entre issues: <em>bloquea</em>, <em>bloqueado por</em>, "
"<em>relacionado con</em>,\n"
"    <em>duplica</em>, <em>duplicado por</em>. Al crear un link, jirrabit "
"añade automáticamente el inverso en el\n"
"    otro issue.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"\nRelationships between issues: <em>blocks</em>, <em>blocked by</em>, <em>related to</em>,\n    <em>duplicates</em>, <em>duplicated by</em>. When you create a link, jirrabit automatically adds the inverse on the\n    other issue."

