msgid ""
"\n"
"    En la barra de búsqueda usa una mini-sintaxis tipo Jira. Ejemplos:\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"\nIn the search bar use a Jira-like mini syntax. Examples:"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Campos soportados: <code>project</code>, <code>status</code>, "
"<code>priority</code>, <code>assignee</code>,\n"
"    <code>reporter</code>, <code>type</code>, <code>label</code>, "
"<code>sprint</code>, <code>epic</code>,\n"
"    <code>text</code>. Operadores: <code>=</code>, <code>!=</code>, <code>~</"
"code> (contiene),\n"
"    <code>in (a,b)</code>. Para los campos de usuario también vale el "
"display name\n"
"    (<code>assignee=\"Erin Soto\"</code>).\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"\nSupported fields: <code>project</code>, <code>status</code>, <code>priority</code>, <code>assignee</code>,\n    <code>reporter</code>, <code>type</code>, <code>label</code>, <code>sprint</code>, <code>epic</code>,\n    <code>text</code>. Operators: <code>=</code>, <code>!=</code>, <code>~</code> (contains),\n    <code>in (a,b)</code>. User fields also accept the display name\n    (<code>assignee=\"Erin Soto\"</code>)."

